{
  "chapter": 5,
  "chapter_summary": "胡铁花因徒手拔出被淬毒的暴雨梨花钉而中毒，楚留香封住其手臂穴位暂缓毒性蔓延。李玉函夫妇提出前往古松庄请一位七指前辈解毒，留下清妙散给楚留香治风寒之症。楚留香突然病倒，二人处境雪上加霜。胡铁花独自守着病重的楚留香，雨夜中一名黑衣蒙面刺客以死猫传书挑衅。胡铁花手持暴雨梨花钉追出客栈，却被对方以调虎离山之计引离，楚留香独留店内毫无抵抗之力。",
  "dialogues": [
    {
      "speaker": "char_liu_wu_mei",
      "speaker_name": "柳无眉",
      "listener": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "text": "楚留香难道怕我这壶酒里也有毒么?",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 6,
      "line_end": 6
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "酒中纵然无毒，他身子里却已有毒了。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 8,
      "line_end": 8
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_yu_han",
      "speaker_name": "李玉函",
      "listener": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "text": "胡兄方才难道已喝下了那杯毒酒?",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 10,
      "line_end": 10
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "这次倒不是酒害了他，而是他的手。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 12,
      "line_end": 12
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_yu_han",
      "speaker_name": "李玉函",
      "listener": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "text": "胡兄是怎么中的毒?",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 16,
      "line_end": 16
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "speaker_name": "胡铁花",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我只怕是撞见了个大头鬼。",
      "tone": "苦笑",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 18,
      "line_end": 20
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "text": "你方才可是用手将那暴雨梨花钉一枚枚自地上拔出来的么?",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 22,
      "line_end": 22
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "speaker_name": "胡铁花",
      "listener": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "text": "嗯!",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 24,
      "line_end": 24
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "text": "这就对了，你以为你的手既没有破，毒气就不会自手上透入，却不知针上的毒已由你指甲缝里透了进去。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 26,
      "line_end": 28
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_yu_han",
      "speaker_name": "李玉函",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "可是，据我所知，这暴雨梨花钉上，从来不淬毒，只因这暗器力道实在太猛，纵然无毒，中人也必死无救。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 30,
      "line_end": 32
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": "char_li_yu_han",
      "text": "李兄话虽说得不错，但这位仁兄却还生怕我死得不够快，所以又在无毒的暴雨梨花钉上淬了剧毒。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 34,
      "line_end": 36
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "speaker_name": "胡铁花",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "上面可是真的有毒么?",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 40,
      "line_end": 40
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_liu_wu_mei",
      "speaker_name": "柳无眉",
      "listener": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "text": "嗯!",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 42,
      "line_end": 42
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": "char_li_yu_han",
      "text": "久闻李老前辈学究天人，虽从不屑以毒药暗器伤人，但对此道却极有研究，李兄家学渊源，所知自也非泛泛之辈可比。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 44,
      "line_end": 46
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "speaker_name": "胡铁花",
      "listener": "char_li_yu_han",
      "text": "不错，你们两口子既然也说钉上有毒，那是万万错不了的了。",
      "tone": "苦笑",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 48,
      "line_end": 50
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": "char_li_yu_han",
      "text": "是以在下想请教李兄，不知这暗器上淬的是哪一种毒?",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 52,
      "line_end": 52
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_yu_han",
      "speaker_name": "李玉函",
      "listener": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "text": "世上毒药的种类实在太多，就连家父只怕也未必能一一分辨得出。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 54,
      "line_end": 56
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "speaker_name": "胡铁花",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "如此说来，我这毒是没法子可解的了?",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 60,
      "line_end": 60
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_liu_wu_mei",
      "speaker_name": "柳无眉",
      "listener": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "text": "谁说没法子?",
      "tone": "轻笑",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 62,
      "line_end": 62
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "speaker_name": "胡铁花",
      "listener": "char_li_yu_han",
      "text": "你们何必瞒我，难道当我是小孩么?你们既然连我中的是什么毒都不知道，又怎么能为我解毒?",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 64,
      "line_end": 64
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "speaker_name": "胡铁花",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你们一个个都哭丧着脸干什么，至少我现在总还没有死呀!来，今朝有酒今朝醉，先痛痛快快喝一顿再说。",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 68,
      "line_end": 70
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "speaker_name": "胡铁花",
      "listener": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "text": "你为什么不让我趁这时候多喝两杯，等我死了，你就算天天将酒泼在我的坟头上，我也连一滴都尝不到了。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 74,
      "line_end": 76
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "text": "我现在已将毒气全都封闭在你手臂里，只要你不喝酒，一个对时之内，毒性就绝不会蔓延……",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 78,
      "line_end": 78
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "speaker_name": "胡铁花",
      "listener": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "text": "一个对时之后呢?在这十二个时辰里，你难道就能找得到为我解毒的人么?",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 80,
      "line_end": 80
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "text": "无论如何，这总比绝望了的好。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 82,
      "line_end": 82
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "speaker_name": "胡铁花",
      "listener": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "text": "好兄弟，你也用不着为我窝窝囊囊的去求人，只要让我把这壶酒喝下去，我一定死不了的。",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 84,
      "line_end": 86
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "speaker_name": "胡铁花",
      "listener": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "text": "你看，这就是我解毒的法子，这法子岂非再好也没有?",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 88,
      "line_end": 88
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "text": "你难道想……",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 90,
      "line_end": 90
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "speaker_name": "胡铁花",
      "listener": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "text": "常言道：蝮蛇噬手，壮士断腕。这没有什么了不起，你又何必大惊小怪?",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 92,
      "line_end": 92
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_yu_han",
      "speaker_name": "李玉函",
      "listener": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "text": "胡兄果然不愧为壮士，只不过……",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 96,
      "line_end": 96
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_liu_wu_mei",
      "speaker_name": "柳无眉",
      "listener": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "text": "只不过你一定要再等十二个时辰。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 98,
      "line_end": 98
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "speaker_name": "胡铁花",
      "listener": "char_liu_wu_mei",
      "text": "为什么?",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 100,
      "line_end": 100
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_liu_wu_mei",
      "speaker_name": "柳无眉",
      "listener": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "text": "只因我已想起了一个可以为你解毒的人。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 102,
      "line_end": 102
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_liu_wu_mei",
      "speaker_name": "柳无眉",
      "listener": "char_li_yu_han",
      "text": "你难道忘了那位只有七根手指的前辈了么?",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 104,
      "line_end": 104
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_yu_han",
      "speaker_name": "李玉函",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "不错，我竟险些忘了，前两天四表弟还曾提起这位前辈，说他老人家已在'古松庄'和熊老伯拼了七天七夜的酒了，还未分出胜负，只要他现在还没有走，胡兄就一定有救了。",
      "tone": "欣喜",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 106,
      "line_end": 108
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_liu_wu_mei",
      "speaker_name": "柳无眉",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "既然还未分出胜负，他就算要走，熊老伯也不会放他走的。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 110,
      "line_end": 112
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "speaker_name": "胡铁花",
      "listener": "char_li_yu_han",
      "text": "古松庄在哪里?熊老伯是什么人?那位七根手指头的前辈又是何许人也?你们说的这些人，我怎地全没有听过?",
      "tone": "好奇",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 114,
      "line_end": 114
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_yu_han",
      "speaker_name": "李玉函",
      "listener": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "text": "这位能老伯虽然和家父那一辈的许多武林前辈都是好朋友，自己却并非江湖中人，胡兄自然没有听起过他。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 116,
      "line_end": 118
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_liu_wu_mei",
      "speaker_name": "柳无眉",
      "listener": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "text": "至于那位七根手指的老前辈，胡兄却一定听过他大名的，只不过他老人家近年为了一件伤心事，已不许别人再提起他的名姓。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 120,
      "line_end": 122
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_yu_han",
      "speaker_name": "李玉函",
      "listener": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "text": "这位老前辈人虽热肠，脾气却十分古怪，若是知道我们在背后犯了他的忌讳，我夫妇只怕就休想再有一天好日子过了。",
      "tone": "苦笑",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 124,
      "line_end": 126
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "speaker_name": "胡铁花",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "此人脾气既如此古怪，又和我素不相识，我若去碰个大钉子回来，岂非比死还难受得多?",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 128,
      "line_end": 128
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_liu_wu_mei",
      "speaker_name": "柳无眉",
      "listener": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "text": "用不着你去碰钉子，我们去就够了，只要我炒两样菜给他吃，他就再也不会拒绝了。",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 130,
      "line_end": 132
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_yu_han",
      "speaker_name": "李玉函",
      "listener": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "text": "不错，可是我们却得快走，古松庄的路虽不远，可也不近，何况，你至少还要在那里弄一个时辰的菜哩!",
      "tone": "轻笑",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 134,
      "line_end": 134
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "speaker_name": "胡铁花",
      "listener": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "text": "两位如此热肠，我若再推三阻四，就不是东西了，可是……老臭虫，你也该陪他去一趟才对。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 136,
      "line_end": 138
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_liu_wu_mei",
      "speaker_name": "柳无眉",
      "listener": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "text": "用不着，楚兄还是……",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 140,
      "line_end": 140
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "speaker_name": "胡铁花",
      "listener": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "text": "你……你……",
      "tone": "颤抖",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 144,
      "line_end": 144
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "speaker_name": "胡铁花",
      "listener": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "text": "你难道也中了毒?",
      "tone": "嘶声",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 148,
      "line_end": 148
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "speaker_name": "胡铁花",
      "listener": "char_li_yu_han",
      "text": "不是中毒是怎么回事?李兄，你……你快瞧瞧他，快……",
      "tone": "焦急",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 152,
      "line_end": 152
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "text": "你难道从未见过人生病么?又何必大惊小怪。",
      "tone": "苦笑",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 154,
      "line_end": 156
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "speaker_name": "胡铁花",
      "listener": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "text": "可是你的身体就像条牛一样，这么多年来，我从来也没有见过你生病，这次怎么会病了?",
      "tone": "焦急",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 158,
      "line_end": 158
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "text": "这次我实在病得不是时候。",
      "tone": "苦笑",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 160,
      "line_end": 160
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "speaker_name": "胡铁花",
      "listener": "char_li_yu_han",
      "text": "从来不生病的人，一病就不轻，李兄你……",
      "tone": "焦急",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 162,
      "line_end": 162
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_liu_wu_mei",
      "speaker_name": "柳无眉",
      "listener": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "text": "你也用不着太着急，我看楚兄这是因为近日劳累过度，又受了风寒，再加上方才为你一着急，就急出病来了。",
      "tone": "柔声",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 164,
      "line_end": 166
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": "char_li_yu_han",
      "text": "不错，这病不……不妨事的，两位还是……还是先去为他找……找解药要紧。",
      "tone": "颤抖",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 168,
      "line_end": 170
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "speaker_name": "胡铁花",
      "listener": "char_li_yu_han",
      "text": "我的毒才不妨事，你们还是先治他的病要紧。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 174,
      "line_end": 174
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "text": "胡说。",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 176,
      "line_end": 176
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "speaker_name": "胡铁花",
      "listener": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "text": "你若不肯让他们先为你治病，就算将解药拿来，我也不吃。",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 178,
      "line_end": 180
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "text": "你活到这么大年纪，怎地还不知轻重!我……我这病就算再等三天再治也没关系，但你的毒却连一时半刻也耽误不得。",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 182,
      "line_end": 184
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_yu_han",
      "speaker_name": "李玉函",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "两位实在义气干云，只不过……",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 188,
      "line_end": 188
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_liu_wu_mei",
      "speaker_name": "柳无眉",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "只不过楚兄这病，最是不能动气，我们若不依他，只有让他的病加重，好在我这里还有些'清妙散'，治这种病最有效。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 190,
      "line_end": 192
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_yu_han",
      "speaker_name": "李玉函",
      "listener": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "text": "不错，楚兄只要每隔两个时辰吃一包，纵然未必就能痊愈，但在我们回来之前，病情是绝不会恶化的。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 194,
      "line_end": 196
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_dian_huo",
      "speaker_name": "店伙",
      "listener": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "text": "客官昨天喝的上好汾酒，小店恰巧还有一壶，还是山西来的原装货。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 206,
      "line_end": 208
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "speaker_name": "胡铁花",
      "listener": "char_dian_huo",
      "text": "老子不是酒鬼，大白天喝什么鸟酒?",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 210,
      "line_end": 210
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "speaker_name": "胡铁花",
      "listener": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "text": "你觉得好些了么?",
      "tone": "担心",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 214,
      "line_end": 214
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "speaker_name": "胡铁花",
      "listener": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "text": "你用不着担心我，我的毒倒不妨事，除了这条膀子被你点住穴道，不能动外，吃也能吃，就跟好人全没有什么两样。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 216,
      "line_end": 218
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "text": "他们还没有回来?",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 224,
      "line_end": 224
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "speaker_name": "胡铁花",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "江湖之中哪里有七根手指的武林前辈?我怎么想也想不出来?以前虽曾有个'七指神偷'，但他却并非只有七根指头，而是右手上多出两根骈指，加起来一共有十二根了，何况，此人非但不会解毒，而且早已死了很久。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 226,
      "line_end": 228
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "text": "如此说来，你认为这夫妻两人是在说谎么?",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 230,
      "line_end": 230
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "speaker_name": "胡铁花",
      "listener": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "text": "他们为什么要说谎?",
      "tone": "轻笑",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 232,
      "line_end": 232
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "speaker_name": "胡铁花",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我只希望他们快些回来才好，否则昨天晚上的那位仁兄若又闯来，我们两个只怕唯有任凭他宰割了。",
      "tone": "苦笑",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 236,
      "line_end": 238
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "他若要来，你关上窗子又有何用?",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 246,
      "line_end": 246
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "text": "有人来了么?",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 266,
      "line_end": 266
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "speaker_name": "胡铁花",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "只不过是只瘟猫而已。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 268,
      "line_end": 268
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "speaker_name": "胡铁花",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "好，你小子要来就来吧!",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 292,
      "line_end": 292
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "speaker_name": "胡铁花",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "虎落平阳，连你这条瘟猫也想来欺负人么?",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 300,
      "line_end": 300
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "speaker_name": "胡铁花",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "朋友你既已来了，有种的就先来和我姓胡的一分高下，躲在黑暗中不敢见人，算不得英雄好汉。",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 330,
      "line_end": 332
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hei_yi_meng_mian_ren",
      "speaker_name": "黑衣蒙面人",
      "listener": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "text": "我早就在这里等着你了，谁叫你瞧不见我。",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 338,
      "line_end": 338
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hei_yi_meng_mian_ren",
      "speaker_name": "黑衣蒙面人",
      "listener": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "text": "你若要和我动手，为何不过来?",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 340,
      "line_end": 340
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "speaker_name": "胡铁花",
      "listener": "char_hei_yi_meng_mian_ren",
      "text": "你既然要杀我，我就在这里，你为何不过来动手?",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 352,
      "line_end": 352
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hei_yi_meng_mian_ren",
      "speaker_name": "黑衣蒙面人",
      "listener": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "text": "我还是在等着你，你又为何不过来?",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 356,
      "line_end": 356
    }
